Support custom Bluesky PDS host in IndieConnector

Adds a `bluesky.host` option (default `bsky.social`) and passes it to
the BlueskyApi constructor so accounts on a non-bsky.social PDS
(e.g. Eurosky) can authenticate against their actual entryway.

Upstream: https://github.com/mauricerenck/indieConnector
Local change: site/plugins/indieconnector/lib/BlueskySender.php

